rComments: I honestly liked his class, would recommend! This professor was pretty good
Loved his class, if you do your work, you will be rewarded for it. Very understanding prof. I would have him as a prof again, but I will be graduating soon.

Dans nos évaluations, certains avaient la même réponse, mais un avait bien et l'autre mal. La plupart ont contesté leurs notes, et ce, à plus d'une reprise. Seule bonne chose c'est qu'il te remet tes points que tu demandes, donc il est facile d'avoir en haut de 90%.

When professors have disrespectful students, they are unable to perform to the best of their abilities.  However, if you embrace his method (however unconventionnal it may be at times) you have the potential to learn concepts with legitimate real world applications.
Avoid him if you can!!! RUN!!!!
